{"tid":637683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國消費者組織呼籲暫停購買中興手機","createTime":"2018-04-22T04:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T12:50:09.000Z","uid":141151,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"43a62fb935085591d2f229a68e1c7868783607ec","tid":637683,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"美國消費者組織呼籲暫停購買中興手機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/22/us-consumer-organization-suggest-stop-buying-zte-phones/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2Fus-consumer-organization-suggest-stop-buying-zte-phones%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e38bc9a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/22/us-consumer-organization-suggest-stop-buying-zte-phones/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部上週日下令美國公司不得向中興通訊提供零部件、軟件和其他技術，作為中興違反和解協議條款的懲罰。很多人關注中興手機未來無法使用 Qualcomm 的處理器，亦不可以使用 Google 的服務和 Android 系統。禁令原來亦影響購買中興手機的客戶，美國有消費者組織就呼籲消費者暫停購買中興手機。<br />\n<br />\n事緣今次禁令將會影響中興為現有 Android 手機提供系統更新，包括修補安全漏洞和保安更新，中興至今未有向消費者作出交代。其中兩間美國電訊商表示，中興沒有通知他們能否繼續提供系統和保安更新，或為手機提供新功能和提升現有功能。消費者組織 Consumer Watchdog 呼籲中興、Google 和電訊商向消費者清楚說明，如果無法確定能否更新，則不應該再銷售新手機。<br />\n<br />\n不少美國的中興手機用戶透過各個渠道嘗試了解和查詢，但全部都得不到中興的回應。除了消費者組織，就連市場研究機構 IDC 的分析師都認為，現時有太多不確定性，因此不應購買中興手機。另一研究機構 Recon Analytics 亦認為就算沒有更新，中興的手機一樣能正常運作，不過用戶會因為無法修補漏洞，令裝置受到安全威脅，消費者將因此受困。<br />\n<br />\n來源：cnbeta"},{"pid":"174dd47d078167eb5b8faa983523ae4d470a421e","tid":637683,"uid":4209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"留俾中国人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97a31b65412602ec63baa3b8eaff4cb416e274f","tid":637683,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb295046cb54d87255f372b61de2a4158b49fb85","tid":637683,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中国又贏"},{"pid":"0b28695c465a0bd8d90e298f78a1fe3a2fa0f092","tid":637683,"uid":53026,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"其實好野唔應該出口，好似日本咁"},{"pid":"2a3e8268adbc168796196ce48c438fe9c2b7e04e","tid":637683,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T08:47:47.000Z","msg":"中國或成最後大贏家"},{"pid":"2e60e32bf8ba050ace81bddbb04a60409965806b","tid":637683,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"中或贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b9fb5b3f6311ad32b932f561793b39244d3226","tid":637683,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:50:57.000Z","msg":"最大贏家出現"},{"pid":"948c338d5308fafd0388ce0be871e0d4fdead54e","tid":637683,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T23:59:21.000Z","msg":"apple 出平價版 iPhone <br />\nmade in US or Mexico<br />\n<br />\n兩國win win 雙贏"},{"pid":"606acbec906aee3af24fd201de5cd5230d751453","tid":637683,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T00:00:57.000Z","msg":"中興執笠除牌, 或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"f0913577eac6a7aa713c594073ec0e75723e4a7c","tid":637683,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T00:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6e8dbdd2c1b6c9cfcf4aa2ba1b04b8d7c61c102","tid":637683,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T00:06:44.000Z","msg":"華為呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edae18a42cb2f0dc8976d17a21aa00860470186","tid":637683,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20b1d8a4566ee567bdec089b63188ef4